<div class="thumbcaption">
<div class="magnify"><a href="/wiki/File:British_Empire_Anachronous_7.png" class="internal" title="Enlarge"><img src="/skins-1.5/common/images/magnify-clip.png" width="15" height="11" alt="" /></a></div>
An <a href="/wiki/Anachronistic" title="Anachronistic" class="mw-redirect">anachronistic</a> map of every territory ever held by the <a href="/wiki/British_Empire" title="British Empire">British Empire</a>.</div>
