<li><a href="/wiki/Qing_Dynasty" title="Qing Dynasty">Qing Empire</a> - 13 million km²<sup id="cite_ref-6" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-6" title=""><span>[</span>7<span>]</span></a></sup> (under <a href="/wiki/Qianlong_Emperor" title="Qianlong Emperor">Emperor Qianlong</a>) -</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/French_colonial_empires" title="French colonial empires" class="mw-redirect">French Empire</a> - 12.3 million km²<sup id="cite_ref-Gordon_5-6" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Gordon-5" title=""><span>[</span>6<span>]</span></a></sup> (under President <a href="/wiki/Albert_Lebrun" title="Albert Lebrun">Albert Lebrun</a> in 1938)</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Portuguese_Empire" title="Portuguese Empire">Portuguese Empire</a> - 10.4 million km²<sup id="cite_ref-Gordon_5-7" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-Gordon-5" title=""><span>[</span>6<span>]</span></a></sup></li>
