<li id="cite_note-USArelEcon-28"><b><a href="#cite_ref-USArelEcon_28-0" title="">^</a></b> Christopher Chase-Dunn. <a href="http://jwsr.ucr.edu/archive/vol11/number2/pdf/jwsr-v11n2-chasedunn.pdf" class="external text" title="http://jwsr.ucr.edu/archive/vol11/number2/pdf/jwsr-v11n2-chasedunn.pdf" rel="nofollow">Social Evolution and the Future of World Society.</a></li>
