<li id="cite_note-30"><b><a href="#cite_ref-30" title="">^</a></b> The combined GDP of the <a href="/wiki/United_Kingdom" title="United Kingdom">United Kingdom</a>, <a href="/wiki/British_Raj" title="British Raj">British India</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ireland" title="Ireland">Ireland</a>, <a href="/wiki/Canada" title="Canada">Canada</a>, <a href="/wiki/Australia" title="Australia">Australia</a>, <a href="/wiki/New_Zealand" title="New Zealand">New Zealand</a>, <a href="/wiki/Ceylon" title="Ceylon" class="mw-redirect">Ceylon</a>, <a href="/wiki/Hong_Kong" title="Hong Kong">Hong Kong</a>, <a href="/wiki/Singapore" title="Singapore">Singapore</a> and <a href="/wiki/South_Africa" title="South Africa">South Africa</a> in 1870 is about $265 billion in Maddison (2006<sup class="noprint Inline-Template"><span title="" style="white-space: nowrap;">[<i><a href="/wiki/Wikipedia:Citing_sources" title="Wikipedia:Citing sources">page&#160;needed</a></i>]</span></sup>).</li>
